# Google Cloud Observability - Security bulletins
The following describes all security bulletins related to Google Cloud Managed Service for Prometheus.
There have been no security bulletins created for Managed Service for Prometheus.
To get the latest security bulletins delivered to you, do one of the following:
- Add the URL of this page to your [feed reader](https://wikipedia.org/wiki/Comparison_of_feed_aggregators) 
- Add the feed URL directly to your feed reader: `https://cloud.google.com/feeds/managed-prometheus-security-bulletins.xml
